    "description": "Are you a skilled Full Stack Developer looking for your next big career move? NIIT Technologies in Amritsar offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout NIIT Technologies:\nNIIT Technologies is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Learning & development budget\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Amritsar, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with NIIT Technologies!",
